metadata.description:
Lion DAO Legend Lioness. There are three tiers of Lion DAO NFTs: 111 Legends, 333 Heroes - of both Lions and Lionesses - along with 3,333 Generations. The rarer the Lion, both by tier and trait, the more doors it opens. Enabling special privileges to those who own it. 

These NFTs have been thoughtfully crafted as character-collectibles and are ready for the interoperable metaverse. The Lionesses all hold potent royal codes and also serve as your immutable membership to the DAO, a ticket to a world of exclusive experiences and surprise drops. Part of Highvibe Network. 

The sounds of the Legends are tuned to the 528 Hz Solfeggio Frequency, which is also referred to as the love frequency. Resonating through the core of everything. Connecting our hearts, our multidimensional nature, and the divine harmony between masculine and feminine energies in all of us. 

/Music by San Ignacio 

/Lead Artist Fernando Chamarelli
metadata.name: Lion DAO Legend Lioness #001
